Unnatural Aura			VISIBLE:YES	KEY:Fetch ~ Unnatural Aura			SORTKEY:Fetch		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:TemplateFeature.Fetch.SpecialQuality	DESC:Animals, both wild and domesticated, can sense the unnatural presence of a fetch at a distance of 15 feet. They will not willingly approach nearer than that and panic if forced to do so; they remain panicked as long as they are within that range.

		

Dead Nerves			VISIBLE:YES	KEY:Gheden ~ Dead Nerves			SORTKEY:Gheden		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:TemplateFeature.Gheden.SpecialQuality	DESC:A gheden has a weak sense of touch and is incapable of feeling pain. It is unaffected by nonlethal damage, stunning, and death from massive damage. This lack of sensation also imposes a -8 penalty on any skill check that involves fine motor control or a sense of touch, such as Open Lock, Sleight of Hand checks, but grants a +4 bonus on Concentration checks provoked by damage.

