Sense Vampires			VISIBLE:YES	KEY:Katane ~ Sense Vampires			SORTKEY:Katane		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:TemplateFeature.Katane.SpecialQuality	DESC:A katane can sense the presence of other katanes, vampires, vampire spawn, and any other form of undead that feeds on living blood within 200 feet. This ability only allows the katane to determine the presence of such a creature in the area, not the number or power of such creatures, and the ability cannot be used to aid in blind-fighting or to pinpoint a target.

